<!-- 

==========================================================================================
                     Steering file template for the pysub framework

                               ==> align-tmp.xml <===

Author: Antonio Bulgheroni, INFN <mailto:antonio.bulgheroni@gmail.com>
Version: $Id: align-tmp.xml,v 1.3 2009-05-19 18:01:01 bulgheroni Exp $
